  <h3>Clone Manufacturers</h3>

  <p>Generic or clone centrifuge manufacturers produce copies of OEM centrifuges that are cheaper but less reliable than the OEM centrifuges.</p>

  <p>These clone centrifuges are typically manufactured in Asian countries (China, Turkey, etc.) and have limited lifespans and single-source spare parts restrictions.</p>

  <p>Read our article <a href="/picking-the-right-industrial-centrifuge/">9 Steps to Selecting the Right Industrial Centrifuge</a> for more information.</p>

