  <h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>

  <p>Industrial centrifuges are some of the most prolific and understated separation equipment. They have applications in almost all processing industries, as described above.</p>

  <p>If any fluid(s) is handled in a specific industry, chances are there is a suitable application for an industrial centrifuge.</p>

